ivardefs.name: approvalDate
ivardefs.desc: The date on which the resource content was approved by the publisher. Approval happens once when the content is officially approved for usage.

ivardefs.name: code_
ivardefs.desc: An identifier for this question or group of questions in a particular terminology such as LOINC.

ivardefs.name: contact_
ivardefs.desc: Contact details to assist a user in finding and communicating with the publisher.

ivardefs.name: copyright
ivardefs.desc: A copyright statement relating to the questionnaire and/or its contents. Copyright statements are generally legal restrictions on the use and publishing of the questionnaire.

ivardefs.name: date
ivardefs.desc: The date  (and optionally time) when the questionnaire was published. The date must change when the business version changes and it must change if the status code changes. In addition, it should change when the substantive content of the questionnaire cha

ivardefs.name: derivedFrom_
ivardefs.desc: The URL of a Questionnaire that this Questionnaire is based on.

ivardefs.name: description
ivardefs.desc: A free text natural language description of the questionnaire from a consumer's perspective.

ivardefs.name: effectivePeriod
ivardefs.desc: The period during which the questionnaire content was or is planned to be in active use.

ivardefs.name: experimental
ivardefs.desc: A Boolean value to indicate that this questionnaire is authored for testing purposes (or education/evaluation/marketing) and is not intended to be used for genuine usage.

ivardefs.name: identifier_
ivardefs.desc: A formal identifier that is used to identify this questionnaire when it is represented in other formats, or referenced in a specification, model, design or an instance.

ivardefs.name: item_
ivardefs.desc: A particular question, question grouping or display text that is part of the questionnaire.

ivardefs.name: jurisdiction_
ivardefs.desc: A legal or geographic region in which the questionnaire is intended to be used.

ivardefs.name: lastReviewDate
ivardefs.desc: The date on which the resource content was last reviewed. Review happens periodically after approval but does not change the original approval date.

ivardefs.name: name
ivardefs.desc: A natural language name identifying the questionnaire. This name should be usable as an identifier for the module by machine processing applications such as code generation.

ivardefs.name: publisher
ivardefs.desc: The name of the organization or individual that published the questionnaire.

ivardefs.name: purpose
ivardefs.desc: Explanation of why this questionnaire is needed and why it has been designed as it has.

ivardefs.name: status
ivardefs.desc: The status of this questionnaire. Enables tracking the life-cycle of the content.

ivardefs.name: subjectType_
ivardefs.desc: The types of subjects that can be the subject of responses created for the questionnaire.

ivardefs.name: title
ivardefs.desc: A short, descriptive, user-friendly title for the questionnaire.

ivardefs.name: url

ivardefs.name: useContext_

ivardefs.name: version

properties.desc: A structured set of questions intended to guide the collection of answers from end-users. Questionnaires provide detailed control over order, presentation, phraseology and grouping to allow coherent, consistent data collection.
